<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      p { margin: 0; } .email-container { font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6; color: #333; } .email-header { background-color:
      #f2f2f2; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      } .email-content { padding: 20px; } .email-footer { background-color:
      #f2f2f2; padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 12px; color: #777; } .reset-button { display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px; color: #fff; background-color:
      #007bff; border: none; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='email-header'>
        <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='email-content'>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Forgot your password?</p>
        <br />
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account.</p>
        <p>Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
        <p><a href='{{reset_link}}' class='reset-button'>Reset Password</a></p>
        <p style='font-style: italic'>
          ⚠️ Note that this link is only valid for 5 minutes
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
          If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.
        </p>
        <p>Thank you!</p>
      </div>
      <div class='email-footer'>
        <p>&copy; 2024 PTIT. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>